{"tid":2230652,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"印和闐！埃及59具古棺出土 開箱2500年前木乃伊畫面曝光","createTime":"2020-10-05T05:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T05:27:34.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac03c90460dee105bc977cb77307afbb632d9924","tid":2230652,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"日前，埃及考古團隊在位於開羅南邊的薩卡拉（Saqqara）古代墓地中，陸續挖掘出2500年<br />\n前的木乃伊古棺，如今已經出土了共59具，而考古團隊也在日前公開「開箱」，向大眾展<br />\n示木乃伊的樣貌，這些棺木不僅外表彩繪顏色依舊鮮豔，就連裡面保存的木乃伊也都十分<br />\n完整。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20201004001876-260809?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fhottopic%2F20201004001876-260809%3Fchdtv&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=0c3ed04e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/hottopic/20201004001876-260809?chdtv</a>"}]}